high_descs: Turn around, head toward the table and turn right to the counter.
Pick up the bowl on the counter.
Turn around, go across the room, turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick the bowl back up.
Turn left and go straight to the counter.
Put the bowl on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and turn to the left to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the bowl up from the counter.
Turn around and cross the room and then go left to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the bowl out again and shut the door.
Go left and stand in front of the counter in front of the coffee maker.
Put the bowl down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the stove.
Pick up the gray bowl on the counter.
Turn around and veer left to the black fridge in the corner.
Place the bowl on the top shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn left and walk to the counter near the coffee maker.
Place the bowl on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl on a counter.
